---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Investment Fee Calculator
description: Estimate how annual investment fees may reduce long-term portfolio growth by comparing balances with and without fees.
navKey: tools
tags: tools
scripts:
  - /assets/tools/investment-fee.js
---

<div class="calculator-page">
    <section class="page-hero page-hero-compact">
        <p class="eyebrow">Cost of investing</p>

        <h1>Investment Fee Calculator</h1>

        <p class="hero-copy">
            Estimate how an annual investment fee may reduce
            the value of a portfolio over time.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section
        class="calculator-card"
        data-investment-fee-calculator
        aria-label="Investment fee calculator"
    >
        <div class="calculator-input-grid">
            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="startingBalance">
                    Starting balance
                </label>

                <input
                    id="startingBalance"
                    type="number"
                    min="0"
                    step="any"
                    value="100000"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="monthlyContribution">
                    Monthly contribution
                </label>

                <input
                    id="monthlyContribution"
                    type="number"
                    min="0"
                    step="any"
                    value="500"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="annualReturn">
                    Annual return before fees
                </label>

                <div class="calculator-input-suffix">
                    <input
                        id="annualReturn"
                        type="number"
                        min="-99.99"
                        step="0.01"
                        value="7"
                        inputmode="decimal"
                    >

                    <span aria-hidden="true">%</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="annualFee">
                    Annual investment fee
                </label>

                <div class="calculator-input-suffix">
                    <input
                        id="annualFee"
                        type="number"
                        min="0"
                        max="99.99"
                        step="0.01"
                        value="0.25"
                        inputmode="decimal"
                    >

                    <span aria-hidden="true">%</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="investmentYears">
                    Number of years
                </label>

                <input
                    id="investmentYears"
                    type="number"
                    min="0.01"
                    step="any"
                    value="20"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                >
            </div>
        </div>

        <p
            class="calculator-error"
            id="investmentFeeError"
            role="alert"
        ></p>

        <div
            class="calculator-results"
            aria-live="polite"
        >
            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Balance without fees
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="balanceWithoutFees"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small>
                    Projected balance before investment fees
                </small>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Balance after fees
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="balanceAfterFees"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small>
                    Projected balance after the annual fee
                </small>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Estimated impact of fees
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="feeImpact"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small id="feeImpactPercent">
                    Difference between the two balances
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-explanation">
            <h2>How investment fees affect growth</h2>

            <p>
                Investment fees may look small when shown as an annual
                percentage, but their effect can grow over long periods.
                Money removed for fees also loses the opportunity to earn
                future returns.
            </p>

            <div class="formula-grid">
                <div class="formula-card">
                    <span>Annual value after fees</span>

                    <code>
                        (1 + return) × (1 - fee)
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <span>Estimated fee impact</span>

                    <code>
                        Balance without fees - balance after fees
                    </code>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>
                The estimated impact includes both the fees deducted and
                the growth those dollars might otherwise have earned.
                Monthly contributions are assumed to be added at the end
                of each month.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <p class="tool-disclaimer">
        For educational purposes only. Results are estimates and assume
        a constant return, constant fee, and regular monthly contributions.
        Taxes, trading costs, fund performance changes, and other expenses
        are not included.
    </p>
</div>
